thread.title: Diane Furstenberg
thread.title_full: Peaches Boutique reviewed by Diane Furstenberg

author: Diane Furstenberg
title: Diane Furstenberg
text: My daughter found the perfect prom dress at a local prom shop. It was more than I wanted to spend so we went online and found the same dress at Peaches Boutique and they were running a Valentines sale so we ended up getting the dress at almost half the price. It was delivered the following week and was in better condition than the one in the local prom store.
